tiles.propagation
Class PropagationComponent

java.lang.Object
  tiles.propagation.PropagationComponent
Direct Known Subclasses:
BlockPropagation, FilterPropagation, IgnorePropagation, MirrorPropagation
public abstract class PropagationComponent
extends java.lang.Object

The base propagation component that defines public methods and encapsulates access to tile state in subclasses.
